tomcat8配置https
1）keytool -genkey -alias sslKeyStore -keyalg RSA -keystore /usr/java/https/keystore/sslKeyStore
名字与姓氏：sso.tks2u.com(域名)
2)导出证书
keytool -export -file /usr/java/https/keystore/sso.crt -alias sslKeyStore -keystore /usr/java/https/keystore/sslKeyStore
3)为客户端的jvm导入证书
keytool -import -keystore /usr/java/jdk/jdk1.8.0_91/jre/lib/security/cacerts -file /usr/java/https/keystore/sso.crt -alias sslKeyStore
密码如果错误，请输入：changeit
4）配置tomcat8的connector（https默认端口是443）
<connector port="443" protocol="HTTP/1.1" sslenabled="true" maxthreads="150" scheme="https" secure="true" clientauth="false" sslprotocol="TLS" keystorefile="bin/.keystore" keystorepass="!@#QWE123qwe">
</connector>